{"tid":1691694,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"你地係咪想太古城嘅事繼續發生","createTime":"2019-11-03T18:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T18:30:31.000Z","uid":246650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47c021cb02153e972667691efc46d55cf0f3bb84","tid":1691694,"uid":246650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:20:07.000Z","msg":"今日發夢有人同我講以下嘅說話，想分享俾大家：<br />\n<br />\n好明顯隻支那曱甴就係探索緊香港人嘅底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而證實我地嘅底線原來仲高撚過國際太空站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日放生一隻，聽日，後日，下星期會有幾多隻？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n22年喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日150個、內地專才、一家團聚、自遊行買撚哂香港啲奶粉，旺區唔係藥房就係金舖呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地肚餓食藥同食金㗎？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胡椒噴霧、胡椒球彈、警棍、催淚彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈、強力白激光電筒、水炮車、點38實彈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我求下你地認真考慮下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多巴絲開po講過好多次嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今日試過得，聽日就會變本加厲</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">仲要有幾多手足出事先醒</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/3454366851291925?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F3454366851291925%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axA1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=01b453dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/3454366851291925?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"5adc011553f1361bb08b3bd6339d765f725836e8","tid":1691694,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:21:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人真係瞓醒繼續起身返工？<br />\n捨得長期三罷未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spYFT9S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspYFT9S.jpg&h=0faf496d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d0afec0d5f47879e8d54797037d4c76e7d592a2","tid":1691694,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:25:49.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8db903786a16adc1f768d109ed0e199948b6c5a0","tid":1691694,"uid":246650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d0db844d3e1e64b447fc16a10b60f1cd685c5c5","tid":1691694,"uid":246650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:29:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f898331546925aa71e72324547e9192b00f238c","tid":1691694,"uid":246650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:29:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bffcb1d86d68f375865954911e1b55e2f2ffb1f6","tid":1691694,"uid":246650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:29:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f938577a5fb46ee0a4abc7c2134f4664c2836b3b","tid":1691694,"uid":